@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### 0a. Registrar usuario owner (para obter token no proximo passo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Owner Board",
  "email": "owner.board.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0b. Login do owner -> 200 com token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner.board.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0c. Registrar usuario nao-membro (para os cenarios de 403/404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Outro Usuario",
  "email": "outro.usuario.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0d. Login do nao-membro -> 200 com token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "outro.usuario.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 1. Criar quadro (usar token do owner) -> 201, BoardMember owner criado
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "name": "Quadro de Marketing"
}

### 2. Listar meus quadros (owner) -> 200 contendo o quadro criado
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

### 3. Obter detalhe como membro (owner) -> 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

### 4. Obter detalhe como nao-membro -> 404 (board.not.found, sem vazar existencia)
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

### 5. Renomear como owner -> 200
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "name": "Quadro de Marketing (renomeado)"
}

### 6. Renomear como nao-owner -> 403 (board.owner.required)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

{
  "name": "Tentativa de renomear"
}

### 7. Excluir como nao-owner -> 403 (board.owner.required)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

### 8. Excluir como owner -> 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

### 9. Criar quadro sem nome -> 422 (validacao de entrada)
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "name": ""
}

### 10. Acessar /boards sem token -> 401 (guard global de JWT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards

### 11. Listar modelos de quadro (change 025) -> 200, 6 modelos com lists[].title
GET {{baseUrl}}/board-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

### 12. Listar modelos sem token -> 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/board-templates

### 13. Criar quadro a partir de um modelo valido -> 201, board com lists+cards populados, owner confirmado
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/from-template
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "templateId": "crm-vendas"
}

### 14. Criar quadro a partir de modelo com nome customizado -> 201, board.name customizado
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/from-template
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "templateId": "scrum-engenharia",
  "name": "Sprint do time X"
}

### 15. Criar quadro a partir de templateId inexistente -> 404 (boardTemplate.not.found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/from-template
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "templateId": "nao-existe"
}

### 16. Criar quadro a partir de modelo sem token -> 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/from-template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": "crm-vendas"
}
